room_title: Escape room "Cele-Break Out!" by Room For Escape in Atlantic City
room_address: 112 Woodland Ave Suite 202 Somers Point, NJ 08244
room_description: A mad party planner thinks your cat, Mr. Riddlesworth, has been spying on his party. He has taken the cat prisoner and it threatening to turn him into a piñata! You’ll have to uncover this planner’s secret plans and codes to find the way to free your cat. But once you’re inside this celebration room you’ll be locked inside unless you find the key to escape. And we only have one hour until the planner returns….
